{"doc":{"isMarkdown":true,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":true,"flaws":{},"title":"数据库","mdn_url":"/zh-CN/docs/Glossary/Database","locale":"zh-CN","native":"中文 (简体)","sidebarHTML":"","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p><strong>数据库</strong>是一种用于收集已组织好的数据以便于搜索、结构化和扩充的存储系统。</p>\n<p>网站开发中，大多数数据库采用关系型数据库管理系统 (RDBMS) 来组织数据，通过 <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Glossary/SQL\">SQL</a>语言来编程。但有些数据库没有遵循上述的组织数据的机制，这类被称作 NoSQL 数据库。</p>\n<p>被广泛使用的服务端关系型数据库有 <em>MySQL</em>（或者源于它的 <em>MariaDB</em>）、<em>SQL Server</em> 和 <em>Oracle Database</em> 等。另一边，出名的 NoSQL 数据库有 <em>MongoDB</em>、<em>Cassandra</em> 和 <em>Redis</em> 等。</p>\n<p>浏览器也有他们特有的数据库系统，被称作 <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Glossary/IndexedDB\">IndexedDB</a>。</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"参见","title":"参见","isH3":false,"content":"<ul>\n  <li>维基百科上的词条 <a href=\"https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/Database\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">Database</a>\n    <ul>\n      <li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Glossary/IndexedDB\">IndexedDB</a></li>\n      <li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Glossary/SQL\">SQL</a></li>\n    </ul>\n  </li>\n</ul>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"参见","id":"参见"}],"summary":"数据库是一种用于收集已组织好的数据以便于搜索、结构化和扩充的存储系统。","popularity":0,"modified":"2022-10-01T03:41:16.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"Database","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"Base de données","locale":"fr","native":"Français"},{"title":"Database","locale":"ja","native":"日本語"}],"source":{"folder":"zh-cn/glossary/database","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/zh-cn/glossary/database/index.md","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/921c46a374ab0a9f4cc809af0370f8c412e54701","filename":"index.md"},"parents":[{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/Glossary","title":"术语表"},{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/Glossary/Database","title":"数据库"}],"pageTitle":"数据库 - 术语表 | MDN","noIndexing":false}}